Southern Union Sets Oct. 11 as Record Date for Merger

-- B y   M i k e   L e e
-- 
2011-09-07T19:20:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/southern-union-sets-oct-11-as-record-date-for-merger-correct-.html
(Corrects description of date in headline and first
paragraph.)  Southern Union Co. (SUG)  set Oct. 11 as
the “record date” for shareholders to be eligible to vote on
its merger with  Energy Transfer Equity LP (ETE) , the Houston-based
company said in a filing today.  Southern Union previously said it will accept Dallas-based
 Energy Transfer ’s $44.25-a-share bid.  To contact the reporter on this story:
